  "Madhukar Parekh is chairman of Pidilite Industries, a company founded by his late father, Balvant Parekh, in 1959.\r\n",
  "He has a minority stake in Pidilite, which is India's leading maker of adhesives and sealants.\r\n",
  "Pidilite's range of products includes construction chemicals, art materials and organic pigments.",
  "His younger brother, Ajay Parekh, also a billionaire, has a board seat."
